description:
Sing Your Face Off is a talent variety competition featuring celebrities who are transformed and trained to perform as a legendary musical icon. Over the course of the series, five celebrities will take on the identity of an iconic music performer. It is based on the Endemol format Your Face Sounds Familiar.




Sing Your Face Off - Season 1, Episode 1

In the series premiere, celebrities Sebastian Bach, Landry Fields, Jon Lovitz, China Anne McClain, and Lisa Rinna each take on identities of different iconic music performers.




Sing Your Face Off - Season 1, Episode 2

RuPaul Charles guest judges as the series' five celebs transform into iconic performers Lady Gaga, Tina Turner and more.




Original Air Date: 31-May-2014
